StringValues.16: A small clay miniature of the town of Timaru. You recognize this item as a traditional Tumerok spell fetish. It can be attached to several different items, each with their own unique use. Alternately, it can be turned into the Tah of Timaru for a reward.
StringValues.14: This item can be used on other objects, but choose carefully...
